        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>This gemstone grants its wearer a +2 item bonus to saving throws.</p>\n<p>Each <em>heartstone</em> is powered by the spirit of a specific night hag. If it's separated from her for 24 hours (or she's been dead for 24 hours), it becomes a nonmagical gemstone. A <em>heartstone</em> allows the hag to use additional occult innate spells: @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Ethereal Jaunt]{Ethereal Jaunt} (9th level) and @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Bind Soul]{Bind Soul} at will, and @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Shadow Blast]{Shadow Blast} twice per day.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> command</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You must be touching the <em>heartstone</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The <em>heartstone</em> attempts to counteract one disease affecting you (counteract level 5, counteract modifier [[/r 1d20+18]]).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> You must be a night hag.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+2 item bonus to saving throws</li>\n</ul>"
